<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Compte validé de {{ adherent.prenom }} {{ adherent.nom }}</title>
  <style>
    /* --- Base --- */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f6fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    /* --- Header --- */
    .header {
      background: #0f1b28;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      max-height: 80px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 15px;
    }
    .header h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* --- Content --- */
    .content {
      padding: 25px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h3 {
      color: #0f1b28;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    /* --- Bloc info --- */
    .details {
      display: inline-block;
      text-align: left;
      background: #f8fbff;
      border: 1px solid #e8eef5;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      margin: 10px auto 5px auto;
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .details p {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #444;
    }
    .label {
      color: #6b7b8e;
    }
    .value {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0f1b28;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    /* --- Bouton CTA --- */
    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 26px 0 8px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0f1b28;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .button:hover { background-color: #0d2c4a; }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    .footer {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
    }
    .footer a { color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; }

    /* --- Mobile --- */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container { margin: 10px; border-radius: 8px; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .header h2 { font-size: 18px; }
      .button { width: 100%; padding: 14px 0; font-size: 17px; }
      .details { padding: 14px; }
    }

    /* --- Preheader (aperçu mail) --- */
    .preheader {
      display: none !important;
      visibility: hidden;
      opacity: 0;
      color: transparent;
      height: 0;
      width: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      mso-hide: all;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Preheader -->
  <div class="preheader">
    Nouveau compte validé sur Wiki Formation : {{ adherent.prenom }} {{ adherent.nom }} ({{ adherent.email }}).
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="header">
      {% if entite.logo %}
        <img class="logo" src="{{ absolute_url(asset('uploads/photos/entite/logo/' ~ entite.logo)) }}" alt="Logo {{ entite.nom }}">
      {% endif %}
      <h2>Compte validé de {{ adherent.prenom }}&nbsp{{ adherent.nom }}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h3>Nouveau compte créé ✅</h3>
      <p>Un nouvel utilisateur a été ajouté sur <strong>{{ entite.nom }}</strong>.</p>

      <div class="details">
        <p><span class="label">Nom complet&nbsp;:</span> <span class="value">{{ adherent.prenom }} {{ adherent.nom }}</span></p>
        <p><span class="label">Adresse e-mail&nbsp;:</span> <span class="value">{{ adherent.email }}</span></p>
        {% if entite.nom is defined and entite.nom %}
          <p><span class="label">Entité&nbsp;:</span> <span class="value">{{ entite.nom }}</span></p>
        {% endif %}
          <p><span class="label">Date&nbsp;:</span> <span class="value">{{ "now"|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</span></p>
      </div>

      {#{% if path('app_administrateur_dashboard') is defined %}
      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="{{ absolute_url(path('app_administrateur_dashboard')) }}" class="button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Ouvrir le tableau de bord
        </a>
      </div>
      {% endif %}#}

      <p style="margin-top:16px;">Merci de votre attention,<br>L’équipe <strong>{{ entite.nom }}</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} {{ entite.nom }}<br>
      <a href="https://wikiformation.fr">wikiformation.fr</a> — contact@wikiformation.fr</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
